{"tid":1242920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［童軍撚］其實繩係好有用既工具","createTime":"2019-06-19T08:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T09:53:19.000Z","uid":237568,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"532613d05b006b0a91e545770dd59bc46c832947","tid":1242920,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:55:59.000Z","msg":"而家政總立法會外面既兩重鐵馬<br />\n係連埋一齊<br />\n用人力去推拉會食胡椒噴霧同警棍<br />\n但我用條夠粗同長既麻繩打個結<br />\n再由所有手足一齊拉<br />\n一定拉得開缺口<br />\n而且和理非既手足都可以幫手拉<br />\n甚至可以好似西部牛仔咁<br />\n套住d狗拉佢地返黎<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"ce3bde80e2c0bc67d33d2f18b0dddbd941740a7b","tid":1242920,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:56:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59ee5f05ba6b7d5d2150833b096d0c2a48401729","tid":1242920,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:56:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"865ea8e64872490f013842360a57b48fb0dcb1f5","tid":1242920,"uid":21544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:56:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b7f08227be80bb808a8d80ab09cfa637c59aa6","tid":1242920,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a69d7cc8626c5428ae580c5c44569eec82e185e4","tid":1242920,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:57:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f6d87cd1d3cf952f7d2c4c77c3c98b63879ce67","tid":1242920,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:57:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01428d29901d4460b89a0e9c318e1902b3b518e8","tid":1242920,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:58:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8cbd3c46030ae27335f3e325894a95b172d1d9e","tid":1242920,"uid":195264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0